Paranoid
========

  The Paranoid::* series of modules are intended enforce safer programming by
providing functions that perform more sanity checks as well as enforcing taint
mode.  Over time I'll add more of my safety hacks to these modules.
  Please see PODs for applicable documentation.  The following PODs are
available:

    Paranoid
    Paranoid::Args
    Paranoid::BerkeleyDB
    Paranoid::Data
    Paranoid::Debug
    Paranoid::Filesystem
    Paranoid::Glob
    Paranoid::Input
    Paranoid::Lockfile
    Paranoid::Log
    Paranoid::Log::Buffer
    Paranoid::Log::Email
    Paranoid::Log::File
    Paranoid::Log::Syslog
    Paranoid::Log::Template
    Paranoid::Module
    Paranoid::Network
    Paranoid::Process

  Please send bugs, requests, and flames to Arthur Corliss
<corliss@digitalmages.com>.
